        "content": "\nMohd Muzzammil, studying in IIT Kanpur as a BT student in CSE will do\nhis summer internship in Associate profile at SAMSUNG Electronics South Korea. Here are some brief\ninsights of his.\n\n## Shortlisted Profiles & Companies:\nGraviton, Systems, Quadeye, Systems\n\n## Insights on the Selection Process\n__Coding Round__\n- All CSE and EE people were eligible\n- Given a single problem and 3hrs to solve it.\n- Largely a brute force question, with some little dp.\n\n__CPI Shortlist__\n- 14 people were shortlist after coding round based on CPI\n\n__Interview__\n- Coding Interview:  Easy question based on a variant of maximum subset problem.\n- HR Interview: They basically try to assess how well may you fit the Korean Culture.\n\n##  Preparation Resources\nInterviewbit and Codeforces\n\n## Advice for students (dos and don’ts)? \nDo Coding and reach out to seniors in case of any help\n\n",
