        "slug": "2022-intern-vishwaraj-singh-piramal-pharma-solutions",
        "content": "\nVishwaraj Singh, studying in IIT Kanpur as a BT student in CHE will do\nhis summer internship in Global Emerging Leader Program - Summer Intern profile at Piramal Pharma Solutions. Here are some brief\ninsights of his.\n\n## Shortlisted Profiles & Companies:\nHUL\n\n## Insights on the Selection Process\n1) Questions were based on general understanding of basics concepts of chemical engineering.\n2) Little knowledge of practical application of Thermodynamics will be helpful. \n3) Thorough understanding of projects and internships written on resume is must. Questions on the core projects and their applications are asked.\n\n##  Preparation Resources\nThermodynamics lecture slides, Fluid mechanic lecture slides \n\n## Advice for students (dos and don’ts)? \n1) Generally have a specific profile in your mind you are targeting and you can prepare for the specific companies coming for that profile. \n2) Be confident with your preparation and your basic concepts in whichever profile you are sitting and the process will be very relaxing.\n3) Don't take tension as internships are the not the end goal for you.\n4) Be confident in the interview, that will help you a lot. \n\n",
