        "content": "\nNandini Ojha, studying in IIT Kanpur as a B.Tech. student in EE will be joining Discovery Inc. as Software Development Engineer-I. Here are some brief\ninsights of hers.\n\n## Shortlisted Profiles & Companies:\nMicrosoft, AmEx, Oracle, Nomura, Discovery\n(Software/Data Analyst roles)\n\n## Insights on the Selection Process\n1. Resume Shortlist\n2. Test\n3. Interview\n\nSample Interview Questions:\n\nLC medium+hard, basics of data structures and DBMS\n\n##  Preparation Resources\nLeetcode, InterviewBit, gfg (coding)\n50 challenging puzzles, brainstellar (puzzles)\n\n\n## Advice for students (dos and don’ts)? \n1. Start prep as early, possibly before PPO announcements\n2. Have a prep buddy + support system (would be nice during interviews :))\n3. Expect chaos. Strive. Good results will follow.\n\n",
