        "content": "\nNandita Gupta, studying in IIT Kanpur as a BT( DM) student in MSE & ECO will be joining Alvarez and Marsal  as Associate. Here are some brief insights of hers.\n\n## Shortlisted Profiles & Companies:\n1. Bain2. Bcg3. Amex4. Accenture5. Barclays6. Capital One\n\n## Insights on the Selection Process\n1. First round - introductory and case study round - standard cases asked previously(usually unconventional case)2. Second round - case study round - Quantitative market entry case and guesstimate3. Third round - exchange of words and interaction with managing director (5-10 mins)informal round\n\n##  Preparation Resources\nCase interviews cracked (IITB case book)Youtube playlist - Aditya Agarwal IIMA\n\n## Advice for students (dos and don’ts)? \n1. Stay calm during the interview process2. Be interactive with the interviewer3. Do not hesitate to ask questions\n\n",
